overview: Music & Musicals, Jazz & Easy Listening, Vocal Pop - Rosemary Clooney showcases her skillful phrasing and dramatic vocal style in this live performance of jazz and pop tunes, exhibiting the versatility for which she's renowned. With a career spanning four decades, Clooney made a name for herself with her interpretations of several novelty songs, earning 13 top 40 hits in the 1950s. This 10-song set includes classics such as "Let's Call the Whole Thing Off" and "After the Ball."
title: In Concert Series: Rosemary Clooney
